Features
Add new tasks with descriptions, priority levels (Low, Medium, High), and due dates.
Edit existing tasks to update their details.
Mark tasks as completed with a single click.
Delete tasks from the list.
Persistent storage in tasks.json to save tasks between sessions.
Modern UI with a light purple-to-white gradient background for a mobile app-like aesthetic.
Input validation for task descriptions and due dates (YYYY-MM-DD format).
Displays tasks in a listbox with their status, priority, and due date.
